Lena.name: Lena
personality_traits: fascination for living plants and mechanical wonders
Lena.profile_text: A young botanist with a fascination for both living plants and mechanical wonders. Determined and curious, spent years piecing together clues to discover the Clockwork Garden. Becomes the bridge between the mechanical and the organic, helping the garden evolve into a new form of life.

Garden Keeper.name: Garden Keeper
personality_traits: communicates in a mixture of mechanical clicks and rustling of leaves
Garden Keeper.profile_text: An ancient automaton who maintains the Clockwork Garden. Covered in moss and vines, with glowing eyes. Speaks with a mixture of mechanical clicks and rustling leaves. Guides Lena and entrusts her to help the garden evolve.
